{
  "chapter": {
    "number": 1,
    "title": "The Day Still Starts",
    "intro_image": "images/chapters/chapter1_intro.png",
    "intro_duration": 3.0
  },
  "episode": 1,
  "title": "Episode 1",
  "events": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "text": "The radiator clicks like a dying insect. Morning exists only because you've decided it does.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event1.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event1_en",
      "soundscape_mp3": "audio/City-of-Dread.mp3",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Get up",
          "next_event": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "Stay seated and think",
          "next_event": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "You stand. Your legs respond out of habit, not will. The floor is coldâ€”concrete pretending to be civilization.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event2.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event2_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Look at the window",
          "next_event": 4
        },
        {
          "text": "Check your belongings",
          "next_event": 5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Thinking has never saved anyone. But you do it anyway. The walls listen, patient and indifferent.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event3.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event3_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Stand up anyway",
          "next_event": 2
        },
        {
          "text": "Stay seated longer",
          "next_event": 6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The window shows you Brno 2157. Towers of grey and green. The revolution's architecture, still standing after everything fell.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event4.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event4_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Look away",
          "next_event": 7
        },
        {
          "text": "Keep watching",
          "next_event": 8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Your jacket. Your ID card. A photo you don't remember taking. These are the fragments you're made of now.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event5.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event5_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Put the jacket on",
          "next_event": 9
        },
        {
          "text": "Look at the photo",
          "next_event": 10
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "Time passes. The radiator clicks. Nothing changes, which is its own kind of answer.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event6.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event6_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Finally stand up",
          "next_event": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "text": "You turn from the window. The room is small. Every room is small when the world outside is too big.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event7.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event7_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Check your belongings",
          "next_event": 5
        },
        {
          "text": "Leave the room",
          "next_event": 11
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "text": "The city moves. Workers. Drones. The same grey tide that rises every morning. You recognize it because you're part of it.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event8.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event8_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Turn away",
          "next_event": 7
        },
        {
          "text": "Open the window",
          "next_event": 12
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "text": "The jacket settles on your shoulders like a question you can't answer. The ID card in the pocket weighs nothing but means everything.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event9.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event9_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Leave the room",
          "next_event": 11
        },
        {
          "text": "Check the window first",
          "next_event": 4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "text": "The photo shows two people. You recognize one of them as yourself. The other is a stranger wearing your face from another life.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event10.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event10_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Put it back",
          "next_event": 9
        },
        {
          "text": "Keep looking",
          "next_event": 13
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "text": "The hallway is concrete and fluorescent. Standard issue. Everything is standard issue when the state decides what you need.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event11.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event11_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Go left",
          "next_event": 14
        },
        {
          "text": "Go right",
          "next_event": 15
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "text": "The window doesn't open. Of course it doesn't. This is Brno 2157. Air is regulated. Freedom is a memory. Windows are decorative.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event12.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event12_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Step back",
          "next_event": 7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "text": "The person in the photo is smiling. When was the last time you smiled? Do you remember? Does it matter?",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event13.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event13_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Put the photo away",
          "next_event": 9
        },
        {
          "text": "Tear it up",
          "next_event": 16
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "text": "Left leads to the stairs. Down is the city. Down is work. Down is the rest of your life, measured in shifts and silence.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event14.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event14_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Go down the stairs",
          "next_event": 17
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back",
          "next_event": 11
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "text": "Right leads to more doors. More rooms. More lives compressed into concrete boxes. The architecture of equality.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event15.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event15_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Keep going right",
          "next_event": 18
        },
        {
          "text": "Turn back",
          "next_event": 11
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "text": "The photo tears easily. Paper always does. Memories are harder. The pieces fall like snow that never reaches the ground.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event16.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event16_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Leave the pieces",
          "next_event": 9
        },
        {
          "text": "Pick them up",
          "next_event": 19
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "text": "The stairs descend into morning. The city waits. It always waits. Patient. Hungry. Indifferent to your choices.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event17.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event17_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Continue down",
          "next_event": 20
        },
        {
          "text": "Stop halfway",
          "next_event": 21
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "text": "A door stands open. Inside, someone's radio plays state broadcasts. The voice is calm. It's always calm. That's how you know it's lying.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event18.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event18_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Keep walking",
          "next_event": 15
        },
        {
          "text": "Listen closer",
          "next_event": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "text": "You gather the pieces. What are you supposed to do with fragments? Build something new? Pretend you can put the past back together?",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event19.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event19_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Keep the pieces",
          "next_event": 9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "text": "You reach the street. Brno stretches out before you. Grey. Green. Inevitable. The day begins whether you're ready or not.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event20.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event20_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Step outside",
          "next_event": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "text": "You stop. The stairs stretch above and below. This is the moment. This is always the moment. Between what was and what will be.",
      "image_link": "images/ep1_event21.png",
      "voice_over": "vo/ep1_event21_en",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "Continue down",
          "next_event": 20
        },
        {
          "text": "Go back up",
          "next_event": 11
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}